Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.52,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人攻来了 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.99,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹 子弹射不准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.55,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵 医护兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 被隔绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.85,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 混账 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是B栋 队长 退路被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:41.77,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,无法过去跟你们会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.80,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 爬也给我爬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.89,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在圆桌室里做死守的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.37,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是最坚固的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.03,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以撑一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里轻易送死 别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.81,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们打开工事 想办法过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.04,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没办法了队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我自己在内 这里尽是伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.88,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.26,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快处理掉 不然会变成食尸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:20.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,水 给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.45,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这能撑多久就撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.37,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,请把防御工事关上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.75,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运 别了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:28.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混账东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 是吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.29,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 想死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.41,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那就尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:47.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是 队长 那么先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:48.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.67,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,堆筑防御工事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.60,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这张大圆桌也反过来做防御工事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好 给我堆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:14.02,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 B栋的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.58,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,救不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.94,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.18,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 我们也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.28,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:28.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再和怪物战斗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.34,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.89,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,因特古拉和阿卡多都抛弃我们不顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.87,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你既出不去 我也不会让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.94,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.43,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.66,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你的坟墓就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.10,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,墓碑就是这幢大得没天理的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.82,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓人就是那位可怕的因特古拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,墓志铭就这样写
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:07:01.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,"了不起的为粉碎纳粹邪恶势力壮烈成仁的佣兵们在此长眠"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.79,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都怪你 成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.41,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你哭哭啼啼地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:13.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,"毫无胆略的混球 像娘儿们似地哭哭啼啼 死得好像虫子那么难看"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.10,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:20.32,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样你也给我死得像样些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:25.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,因为兴趣来赚钱 因为兴趣来打仗的吧 兵士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.29,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就为了兴趣战斗直到死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck Fuck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:37.25,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,何况还没到一定会死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.83,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是负责Defence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.83,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(500,446)}防御
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,快把防御工事垒好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.32,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,负责Offence的人正在赢取得分反败为胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.32,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,449)\fs20}攻方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.23,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋家伙 给我打中 可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.20,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.12,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来 你们这些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.37,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不许逃跑 战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.91,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:20.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.05,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧 燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.76,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,全杀光 全杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Hellsing的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.44,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也叫王立国教骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.30,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.78,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,杂碎 很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.85,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.03,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:36.74,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 您回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,米 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.77,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.57,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,表情这么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.48,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉 这是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 这也是幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.18,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.81,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 连你也是幻象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:37.23,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,全是骗你的 彻底骗你的 笨蛋不死是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.66,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,上士 那边情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:51.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这个酸味是 A型RH阴性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.03,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 这次猜对了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.67,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 完全正确 全中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.39,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真猜得准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,口感不同啊 口感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:06.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.04,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吞进喉头的感觉不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 A型血很不同 要形容的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:10.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 那些家伙 要把那些家伙全部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,全都干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.68,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛 我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把那边的椅子带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.70,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,堵上 快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,快修好防御工事 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.78,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 身体不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.50,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.28,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 已经撑不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 混账家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.62,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就算投降 我们也全都会被折磨死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.93,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的子弹重新分配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:16.14,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 用这个 这些用完可就打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.24,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,作过法的银弹已经用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.83,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.19,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了 眼睛看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.63,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.60,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.94,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.94,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就和那时完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.72,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,乌干达崴得机场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.69,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,机场右翼阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那次幸好援兵及时赶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 可恶 撑不下去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别说丧气话 副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.57,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.63,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 火箭炮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.14,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟然还有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.99,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,副队长 伤亡情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.34,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,副队长 喂 副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了 能让我先去休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.60,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.48,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,命中 要突击进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.15,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.60,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再发一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.16,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,火炮就剩一枚了 是不是该省着点用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:11.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 发射吧 先干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.81,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,将那些可悲的家伙轰成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:17.78,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Jawohl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:17.78,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(427,445)}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.85,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:41.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:06.05,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,直接火炮支援 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.74,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:16.28,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,如约赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.42,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩真的赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.96,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,单枪匹马杀光了所有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:31.64,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 她果然是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.44,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.31,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是强迫也该好好吻她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉斯 塞拉斯·维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.80,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩你一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:04.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉 是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.43,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:22.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这是幻觉 这是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.64,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉斯又制造麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:34.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她用石块砸了一个抢别人玩具的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.31,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉 是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟所有的老师都合不来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.49,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那件事依然对她影响很深
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:46.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果再惹麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.00,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这家孤儿院恐怕就不能再收留她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.47,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再深入些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.58,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想当警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.15,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,没有考虑过其他的路途吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:05.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太顽固了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.33,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你父亲确实是为好警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.42,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还有别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你这完全是固步自封 抹杀了全部潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.41,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,只是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.52,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再深入 再深入些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.23,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 塞拉斯 好好听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.67,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要走出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.96,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了吗 挂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.81,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 挂了吗 臭警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了吧 死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.20,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,死得很彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:08.01,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,臭警察 你这个臭警察现在后悔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:12.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,小小警员管太多就是这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.88,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼 畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起来 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.40,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.64,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心 我要玩她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.32,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 都已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.28,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 还是热的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.89,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning！塞拉斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.89,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(340,445)}早安!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.55,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,想必做了个好梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,还有条手臂 另一条手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.74,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个顽强的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:21.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你是虫子吗 还是青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:41.37,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 和传闻的完全不同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.52,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾 没用的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:55.39,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多该送你上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:59.55,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候该取你的首级了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:04.43,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 丑女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.49,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:15.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,送你颗子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 丑女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:38.76,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:41.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,往这边 快 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.57,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔……队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:51.50,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:37.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.59,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,请别管我了 你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:55.26,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.77,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:48.43,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾 身为垃圾做什么无谓挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.33,0:24:52.43,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:24:54.09,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.86,0:25:01.32,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.58,0:25:03.68,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:14.77,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,赶来救我的你却反而被我给救了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.08,0:25:37.33,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.70,0:26:10.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你发呆的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.19,0:26:14.69,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.10,0:26:19.45,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔……
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.44,0:26:21.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 塞拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.44,0:26:24.30,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是个坚强的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.78,0:26:26.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:29.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我 然后一起干掉敌人吧 塞拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:38.67,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不是叫你不要哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.04,0:26:50.82,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你就家伙 眼睛被人弄瞎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:52.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.64,0:26:56.57,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂也被砍了 体无完肤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.95,0:27:00.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.13,0:27:06.22,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.64,0:27:10.00,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是个好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.41,0:27:16.11,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,为保护这家伙而死 也无憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.98,0:27:27.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:29.31,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.63,0:27:30.86,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.19,0:28:22.93,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你让她哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.25,0:28:29.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,既是垃圾一样的虫子身份
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.25,0:28:31.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,到处乱飞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.95,0:28:33.10,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.78,0:28:40.80,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们刚刚做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:43.81,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们要怎么偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:47.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是援军 别动队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.35,0:28:48.83,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 小虫子们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.28,0:28:51.34,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一只手捏死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:57.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子们的生命到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.54,0:29:10.25,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗 又来了吗混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.79,0:29:14.02,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个人是小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.55,0:29:18.52,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你说他是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.47,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饶了你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.36,0:29:31.52,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.49,0:29:34.75,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:37.67,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.43,0:30:01.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}あなたを刻んで確かめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.43,0:30:01.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}想要将你铭刻来确认你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.10,0:30:05.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.10,0:30:05.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}想要看见
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.93,0:30:25.42,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}磨いた桐棚の上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.93,0:30:25.42,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}在磨损的货架上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.14,0:30:31.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.14,0:30:31.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}碎裂地
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:36.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}並べて
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:36.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}并列着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:50.63,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧 贝尔纳多特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.86,0:30:52.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.27,0:30:57.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.49,0:31:01.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.69,0:31:04.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的招术被…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.53,0:31:06.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,共赴战场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.86,0:31:11.00,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,将他们 一起将他们全都干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.97,0:31:17.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}そこにあたしは棲んでる?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.97,0:31:17.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}我栖身此处吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.88,0:31:14.55,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.08,0:31:16.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.37,0:31:18.87,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那些Vampire士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.37,0:31:18.87,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(422,444)}吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.28,0:31:22.02,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在战场上耀武扬威不惧炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:29.96,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}あたしの片方は生きてる?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:29.96,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}我的那一半是否仍活着
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:24.84,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,身经百战的武装亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.80,0:31:28.88,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,在害怕眼前的一个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.90,0:31:33.25,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在害怕一个浑身是伤的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.37,0:31:35.84,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙到底
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.26,0:31:37.06,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.19,0:31:41.05,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪 开枪 快开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.56,0:32:10.84,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}おさえたら恐い?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.56,0:32:10.84,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}抑制的话会不会害怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.32,0:32:09.18,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.45,0:32:11.35,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,真的糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.32,0:32:18.14,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}少しずつだから
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.32,0:32:18.14,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}一点一点地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:14.24,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不明白为什么会变成这种情形
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.83,0:32:16.77,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真的糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:23.48,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}切り開いて胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:23.48,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}在切开的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.81,0:32:33.56,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}舌(した)を這(は)わせたいだけなの
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.81,0:32:33.56,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}只想卷起舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.61,0:32:43.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}そとはうっとりと透明にすました膜
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.61,0:32:43.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}外面是出神入化透明的膜
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.69,0:32:49.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an7}うちは黒(くろ)紫色(むらさきいろ)に熱気(ねっき)をおびて
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.69,0:32:49.95,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}里面是黑紫色带着热度
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.69,0:32:50.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.16,0:32:54.92,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,要我一滴一滴 一毫升一毫升慢慢吸尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:56.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,要吸尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:57.51,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.84,0:33:12.54,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,深入 深入
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.02,0:33:17.37,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,深入 更深入 再深入些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.02,0:33:19.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再深入些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.98,0:33:22.76,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:23.93,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.42,0:33:27.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人 不是这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:29.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是谁 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.86,0:33:32.00,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 这些 不是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.46,0:33:33.87,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是记忆 是心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.23,0:33:35.13,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.58,0:33:37.19,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.60,0:33:38.89,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.61,0:33:42.59,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.21,0:33:46.94,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫他作虫子的那个男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.15,0:33:50.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓血液是衡量灵魂价值的货币
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.51,0:33:51.83,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是意识的银币
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.17,0:33:56.85,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血和给予血液就是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.36,0:33:58.47,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.13,0:34:02.58,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.12,0:34:04.85,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,薛定谔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.11,0:34:07.33,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.63,0:34:12.97,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处不至也哪儿都不在 索林
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.38,0:34:15.56,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来给少校传话的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.79,0:34:18.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,现在宣令
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.39,0:34:22.20,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,少校说‘制敌机先乃用兵之道’
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.60,0:34:23.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.95,0:34:24.78,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.29,0:34:31.80,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,‘果断处置违反军令造成损兵折将的无能部下\N是身为指挥官的为官之道’
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.26,0:34:33.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,但是么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:38.56,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你本应已受处决
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.03,0:34:43.08,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,少校和博士刚弄到了个超有趣的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.25,0:34:48.03,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,正玩得起劲 所以没空管你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.85,0:34:54.04,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怪物 既是塞拉斯·维多利亚 也非塞拉斯·维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:58.44,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你的处罚就由这个Vampire来执行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:58.44,Notes,RP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(517,445)}吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.64,0:35:00.62,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.24,0:35:13.16,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.64,0:35:15.07,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.45,0:35:29.64,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.41,0:35:33.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.90,0:35:35.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.56,0:36:42.49,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.23,0:36:45.34,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要走 要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.76,0:36:49.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我和队长约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.32,0:36:52.53,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.84,0:37:00.58,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要出发去打倒他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.83,0:37:06.87,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:10.49,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 你虽然殒命于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.39,0:37:12.36,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.92,0:37:17.22,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其实你就在那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.81,0:37:20.65,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.91,0:37:35.02,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:36.15,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.28,0:37:58.01,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空泛起鱼肚白
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.69,0:38:00.12,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就快天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.29,0:38:06.27,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后 连阳光也将毫不计较地化作弦上之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.54,0:38:07.38,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,激射而出
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.60,0:38:09.98,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,向着死都
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.42,0:38:18.93,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明的出击
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.27,0:43:25.55,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:28.76,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我想看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.62,0:43:32.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.56,0:43:34.82,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,索林死了啊少校
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.28,0:43:36.57,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,死得像只虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.49,0:43:39.90,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.09,0:43:41.72,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.36,0:43:45.73,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,覆亡开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.25,0:43:48.21,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,真为此高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.12,0:43:51.17,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,您可真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.52,0:43:53.71,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,耍着每个人团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.92,0:43:58.00,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了让大家一个不漏地去攻击地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:04.20,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓战争即是如此这般
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.78,0:44:06.45,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓地狱即是此地
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.12,0:44:12.61,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,我在无限地掠夺和被掠夺
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.78,0:44:16.46,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限地摧毁也在被无限地覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.05,0:44:24.24,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为此我才能超越野心的白昼和悟道的夜晚而此刻站立在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.87,0:44:25.66,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:29.12,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,覆亡就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.57,0:44:32.56,Hellsing,RP,0000,0000,0000,,和胜利一起

